    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333 hp with a razor-sharp 8,000 RPM redline via six individual throttle bodies. The powertrain is mated to a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and an M Variable Differential Lock for optimal torque distribution. Mechanically flawless, this vehicle has undergone a comprehensive subframe reinforcement and a proactive rod bearing replacement. The double VANOS system has been overhauled to ensure factory-spec timing and throttle response. The chassis remains taut, riding on OEM Style 67 forged wheels with no curb rash. This is a turn-key, investment-quality specimen for the discerning enthusiast who demands mechanical perfection and historical authenticity.",
